The BERGER routing scheme is in networklayer/manetrouting. 
My implementation is based on inet (v 2.1.0), omentpp 4.2 is needed to pre-installed

OMNeT++ should be installed to run the routing schemes.
OMNeT++ (https://omnetpp.org/) is OMNeT++ is an extensible, modular, component-based C++ simulation library and framework, primarily for building network simulators.

